<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/resources/demos/style.css">

</head>
<body>

<div class="jumbotron">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>User Dashboard</h1>
        <p> Showing details about your user account.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

<div class="container">
<p><%= notice %></p>

<h4>DESCRIPTION OF PROGRAM</h4>
Dig In Rewards gives you cash back for your purchases while automatically donating to a cause of your choice.  The innovative program is designed to give consumers incentives for their loyalty to businesses, while supporting their favorite cause.</P>

<p>Retailers give a percentage of every transaction as cash back to our member and to our member's cause.<p>

<hr>

<H5>Have you recently made a purchase from one of our partners?</h5>
<p>If so, create a transaction below.  Fill in the details and take a picture of your receipt.  We'll do the rest for you.<p>
<p><a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg btn-block" href="/transactions/new" role="button">Create new transaction &raquo;</a></p>

<HR>

<div class="table-responsive">
  <table class="table">
  <thead>
  <tr>
    <th>Total Cash from Retailers</th>
    <th>Payments To <%= current_user.username %></th>
    <th>Current Balance</th>
    <th colspan="3"></th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
  <tbody>
  <% @user_balances.each do |item| %>
      <tr>
        <% total_credits = item.total_credits || 0 %>
        <% total_debits = item.total_debits || 0 %>
        <% balance = total_credits - total_debits %>
        <td><%= number_to_currency(total_credits) %></td>
        <td><%= number_to_currency(total_debits) %></td>
        <td><%= number_to_currency(balance) %></td>
    <% end %>
  </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<h4>LIST OF TRANSACTIONS</h4>
		<% @transactions.each do |transaction| %>
			<%= transaction.transaction_date %>, <%= transaction.retailer.name %>, <%= number_to_currency(transaction.amount) %><br>
		<% end %>
	<b>TOTAL SPENT:   
		<% @transaction_totals.each do |transaction| %>
			<% id = transaction.user_id %>
	        <% total_transactions = transaction.total_transactions || 0 %>
	        <%= number_to_currency(total_transactions) %>
	    <% end %> </b>

<br><br>

<h4>CAUSE DONATIONS</h4>
		<% @transactions.each do |transaction| %>
			<%= transaction.transaction_date %>, <%= transaction.cause.name %>, <%= number_to_currency (transaction.cause_split * transaction.amount) %><br>
		<% end %>
	<b>TOTAL DONATIONS:  XXXXX </B>

<hr>

<h5>CAUSE INFORMATION</h5>
<% cause = Cause.find(current_user.cause_id) %>
<p>You are currently signed up to donate to  <b>"<%= cause.name %>"</b> as your preferred cause.  If you would like to change your cause, update it in your USER PREFERENCES.<p>

<P>LIST OF CURRENT CAUSES IN THE PROGRAM<p>

<p>REQUEST TO ADD A CAUSE</P>

<hr>

<p>LIST OF CURRENT BUSINEESES IN THE PROGRAM<P>

<p>LINK TO WORDPRESS DIRECTORY</P>

<p>REQUEST TO ADD A BUSINESS</P>

<hr>

<p>RSS FEED OF RECENT NEWS</P>

<p>RSS FEED OF RECENTLY ADDED BUSINESSES</P>

<HR>

<p>INVITE SOMEONE TO JOIN</P>

</div>

<br>
<br>

<%= yield %>

</body>

<hr>

</html>